			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Wu's gauntlets are definitely great gloves for a monk below level 20. But I disagree that they are the best all the way to 30. As one example, consider Lupine Claw Gauntlets made from a werewolf claw and 75 plat. They are AC 4 and add +3 to AGI + DEX. They weigh 0.9 more then Wu's Gauntlets, but I don't know any monks who feel that +6 to their primary stats is not worth a little extra weight.<BR>
Brother Boston<BR>
Rodcet Nife
